WEBVTT

00:02:29.880 --> 00:02:32.720
You will have to learn 
the interface for each app.

00:02:33.240 --> 00:02:37.270
All day you will be on the endless 
controllers, typing and swiping.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:40.770
My life is already complicated enough

00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:44.160
I don’t want to learn how to
communicate with all these devices.

00:02:44.280 --> 00:02:46.540
Why don’t they learn to speak with me?

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:51.560
When I talk to you, I don’t need 
to touch you or swipe you,

00:02:52.170 --> 00:02:54.200
I just speak and get the point across,

00:02:54.200 --> 00:02:58.040
you understand and get back 
to me with your answer.

00:02:58.040 --> 00:03:00.120
Why don’t our bots do that as well?